more than a month ago , the chinese government resumed the exercise of its sovereignty over macao .
this is a great event of the chinese nation , which happened after hong kong 's return to the motherland , marking a new stage in the great cause of the reunification of the motherland .
the solving of the taiwan issue has been placed more prominently before us .
further studying and implementing the important speech by president jiang zemin entitled " continue to strive to promote the accomplishment of the great cause of the reunification of the motherland " will be of paramount importance to enhancing our sense of historical responsibility for the reunification of the country and a sense of urgency , to guiding us to do a good job in the cross - century work with taiwan , and realizing the complete reunification of the motherland and the comprehensive rejuvenation of the chinese nation .
they urged the taiwan authorities to seize the opportunity and make bona fide response .
despite the ups and downs in the situation across the taiwan straits over the past five years , the compatriots at home and abroad , inspired and propelled by president jiang 's speech , made common efforts to boost cross - strait relationship through a tortuous course . seen from the contacts and exchanges between macao and taiwan , since the opening of navigation between macao and taiwan in $date , the number off taiwan compatriots coming to macao had increased from $number $date to $number $date , a $number - fold increase .
