vice information lu xinkui of information industry said that structural contradictions have constantly been a major problem affecting the sound development of the information industry .
due to the lack of effective macro - control measures , some localities and departments vied with one another to develop products in great demand ; thus the phenomena of blind investment and redundant construction still survive despite repeated prohibitions .
the communication service and network structures are not reasonable enough . there are only a few large group companies in china which have competitive power on the international market . besides , china has an excess production capacity of low - and medium - grade products and relies mainly on imports to develop value - added products . lu xinkui urged : the responsible departments at various levels should work in line with actual conditions .
according to the industrial policies , the priorities in developing information products , and the local realities , the information industry should bring into play the functions of its new growth points , work with purposes , lay stress on key points , accurately define ways for development , and maintain its vigor and vitality .
