a county deals with the work in various areas , such as politics , economy , and culture . so , county ( city ) leading cadres should study all branches of learning , including theories , modern economy , science and technology , laws , management , and history . only by so doing will they be able to achieve their work .
jiang zemin pointed out that unswervingly implementing the party 's line , policies , and principles to the letter and resolutely carrying out the party 's line , policies , and principles despite repeated setbacks are basic political demands on all leading cadres .
there are $number counties ( cities ) in china . each county has its own actual conditions . so , we cannot ask all of them to follow the same pattern in implementing the central policies and principles and carrying out the work in all areas .
only when counties proceed from their actual conditions and work closely in line with local practice will they realistically be able to implement the central policies and principles to the letter . in regard to the importance of the work of going deep to reality and the masses , jiang zemin said that in the face of plenty of tasks related to the urban and rural areas and the grass roots and having direct contacts with the masses , county ( city ) leading cadres should be keen in reflecting the feelings and will of the people .
