the six wanted criminals were : wu yung - yi , a $number - year - old man who had previously been convicted of a series of crimes , including injury to others , attempted murder , use of firearms , robbery , smuggling , and so on , had smuggled with a fishing boat some $number kg of amphetamine in collaboration with chiang a - sheng and some others in $date .
after the case was exposed , wu and chiang fled to the mainland ; li hsi - huang , a $number - year - old suspect who had previously been convicted of crimes like manslaughter , larceny , and so on , had been arrested by the mainland last $date while he was driving a boat from quemoy to illegally enter the mainland ; chou shu - jen , a $number - year - old suspect who had previously been convicted of crimes like drug abuse , injury to others , and so on , had fled to the mainland but was arrested by the mainland public security personnel last $date while he was taking drugs ; yang wen - lung , a $number - year - old suspect who had previously been convicted of crimes like gambling , document forgery , fleeing , and so on ; chen tien , a $number - year - old man who had previously been convicted of crimes like obstructing military service , smuggling , deception , and so on ; he yung - ming , a $number - year - old suspect who had previously been convicted of larceny .
