underwater long $date is a matter of life and death .
for months , the officers and men - fighting with the stormy waves , keeping away from hidden reefs and crossing island chains deep down the ocean - had been exploring the way in unfamiliar waters , venturing into " deadly sea areas , " and struggling with pacific storms .
this is a test of the ultimate limit of the submarine , the crew , and the weapons .
