at the start of the new year , the public security contingent building , a long - standing focus of attention of all walks of life in the society , has made a major stride forward .
the public security ministry today decided to introduce some $number forceful , quick - yield , user - friendly , and easy - for - mass - supervision measures with an eye on bringing about a fundamental turn for the better in the face of the public security contingent through unremitting efforts over the next three years or so .
moreover , as of $date of this year , the police service " $number " hotline shall accept the mass supervision and complaints . people who identify law - violation , discipline - violation , or dereliction - of - duty behavior with public security organs or personnel or people 's policemen may directly dial " $number " for supervision or complaint purposes .
meanwhile , the system of making police affairs public shall be further perfected ; a people 's report feedback system shall be introduced ; a system of publicly handling and passing verdicts on public order cases and traffic accidents shall be enforced ; a unified people 's policemen examination and recruitment system shall come into force in the public security organs across the country ; a system of appointing cadres through competition ; sending people 's policemen with poor scores to undergo training ; and relocating or laying off policemen in the lowest positions shall be enforced ; a leading cadre qualifying examination and assessment system shall be introduced in the public security organs ; and the work of exchanging or rotating cadres in different posts shall be stepped up .
public security minister jia chunwang pointed out at a news briefing held today : the public security organs at all levels must adhere to the guiding principle of taking the initiative to grasp problems in real earnest and on an earlier date and should firmly keep the initiative in work .
grasping problems in real earnest does not mean staging a show for the leaders and masses . rather , it means daring to crack hard nuts in real earnest ; taking the initiative to expose contradictions ; and eliminating interference from all sides . we must never be tolerant or accommodating to and shield or cover up problems within our ranks and nor should we try to turn big problems into small ones and small ones into no problems at all .
in order to grasp problems on an earlier date , we should work hard to identify and tackle problems of tendencies and symptoms of problems and exert our utmost to resolve the problems in the embryonic stage .
in order to take the initiative to grasp problems , the public security organs must take the initiative to grasp on their own the problems relating to the public security contingent building and the public security personnel rather than wait for the masses to report , the leaders to issue instructions on , or the news media to expose such problems .
jia stressed : the public security organs at all levels should take the initiative to accept supervision from the people 's congresses , the cppcc [ chinese people 's political consultative conference ] committees , the people and masses , and the news media ; should further establish and perfect various systems under which the public security organs enforce the law ; handle cases ; or administer and manage public order ; and should work hard to block up through mechanisms and systems the loopholes through which negative or corrupt problems crop out .
an official from the ministry of foreign trade and economic cooperation [ moftec ] here indicated that the two sides are still in talks on technical issues , adding that so far no breakthrough has been made .
he remained optimistic about the prospects for the negotiations , however .
when asked whether the focus of the negotiations was on telecommunications issues , the official said that it was not completely true .
