setting up the social security system and giving housing subsidies affect the people 's feelings the setup of the social security system is an auxiliary reform , as well as a basic reform .
at present , there are $number laid - off workers from state - owned enterprises and $number retirees nationwide .
last year , basic living expenses were distributed to $number percent of the laid - off workers , and the majority of the localities ensured to pay $number percent of the old - age pensions in full and on schedule .
