he listened to the report of the jingyang county party committee on the situation of the party building and the preparations for the " three stresses " education , held a discussion participated in by the county 's leading cadres and personalities from various quarters , went deep into the rural areas to listen to the opinion of the village cadres and peasants , and attended a meeting on the " three stresses " education among the leading cadres of jingyang county , at which he made a mobilization speech .
he stressed that as jingyang was once the site of the red army 's headquarters , we should carry forward the fine tradition and style of the old revolutionary base areas and do a good job of the " three stresses " education in the spirit of yanan rectification movement .
