cao gangchuan noted : under the correct leadership of the party central committee , the state council , and the central military commission , china 's scientific and technological undertaking for national defense has realized a historic leap of growing out of nothing and expanding from weak to strong and from small to large ; and has brought true an epoch - making change in the weaponry development of the pla from manufacturing on imported models to designing and manufacturing weapons on our own , from developing conventional weapons to sophisticated weapons , and from developing weapons for the ground force only to weapons for all arms .
