a batch of battleships , aircraft , land weapons , precision - guidance missiles , and electronic telecommunications equipment of advanced performance has been successfully developed and used to equip our troops .
today , our army has developed a basic system for its weaponry and equipment of a new generation , which enjoys a relatively intact structure and a relatively strong capacity of developing complete sets of weaponry and equipment , thus providing strong weaponry and technological support for our army to enhance its defense and combat capabilities under modern technological , especially high - tech , conditions .
meanwhile , breakthroughs have also been made in the project of manned space flight .
our study and research of high technologies has successfully shortened our gap with the world 's advanced level , and has provided both a technological source and a strong driving force for efforts to accelerate the weaponry modernization of our army .
cao gangchuan indicated : such a large - span development in the scientific and technological undertaking for national defense and weaponry development has also brought along the progress of the entire country in the field of high technologies ; given a great impetus to the industrialization of such high - tech sectors as nuclear power , aviation , space flight , shipbuilding , machinery , and electronics ; and has made considerable contribution to promoting the economic construction and enhancing the comprehensive national strength of our country .
we should further carry forward and develop the elated enthusiasm and the high spirit of struggle that prevailed in those years when we were engaged in the development of " two bombs and one satellite " ; constantly make innovations , constantly scale new heights , and constantly attain new progresses in promoting scientific and technological advances for our national defense and weaponry development ; and strive to open up a new prospect in the scientific and technological undertaking for national defense and weaponry development .
