beijing , $date ( xinhua ) - - $number national people 's congress [ npc ] and its standing committee have continuously strengthened the legislative work over the past year , with a total of $number draft laws examined and $number of them approved . the annual target of legislative work was thus achieved , and the endeavor of initially forming a socialist legal system with chinese characteristics during this term was moved forward .
the legislative work of $number npc and its standing committee over the past year had the following features : the legislative work was done in coordination with the state 's important policymaking on reform , development , and stability , aiming to ensure and enhance smooth development of the economic construction and all the social undertakings through the establishment and perfection of related law systems .
with the administrative reconsideration law being enacted , and , together with the existing administrative lawsuit law , the law on the state compensation , and the administrative supervision law , a supervision and restriction mechanism for the state 's administrative power was initially formed . the npc standing committee also stipulated the decision of banning heretic organizations and preventing and punishing heretic activities . this move was of great meaning in terms of safeguarding social stability .
the standing committee has also examined the draft legislation law .
another characteristic of the legislative work of the npc and its standing committee in the past year was the strengthening of law revision .
half of the draft laws examined and discussed by the npc and its standing committee in the past year were revisions of laws , including the individual income tax law , accounting law , highway law , criminal law , and company law .
in line with the needs continuously emerged from the course of development of reform , opening up , and modernization drive , the npc and its standing committee revised laws with good timing , thus making the laws better fit into the objective reality and play a stronger role in setting up norms for social life .
the other characteristic of the legislative work of the npc standing committee in the past year was to bring the explanations of laws into the agenda of the standing committee meetings .
besides explaining the regulations related to the basic law of the hong kong special administrative region , the npc standing committee also examined the draft explanation related to the criminal law .
explanation of law boosts the usability of law , which is advantageous to the safeguarding of the authority of law and the unification of legal systems .
