beijing , $date - - ten departments and organizations , including the general office of the central guidance committee of spiritual civilization construction , ministry of civil affairs , ministry of public security , ministry of construction , ministry of culture , state administration of physical culture and sports , cyl central committee , all - china federation of women and china association for science and technology , recently held a teleconference on deeply launching activities of " stressing civilization and fostering new practices . "
the conference planned activities for " stressing civilization and fostering new practices " this year based on work arrangements made by the central guidance committee on ethical and cultural construction .
the conference held that activities of " stressing civilization and fostering new practices " personally championed by general secretary jiang zemin had achieved obvious results in resolving salient problems of decorum in words and deeds , environmental hygiene , quality of service and transport order , as well as in " showing warmth and concern " to workers laid off from state - owned enterprises , " protecting the ecological environment and promoting civilized new practices , " and other respects . with the energetic support of party committees , governments and relevant departments at various levels , they attracted active participation from various trades and professions and from the broad masses of the people , and produced quite a widespread impact on the community .
the conference pointed out : launching activities of " stressing civilization and fostering new practices " in depth is an urgent need for promoting reform and development and maintaining social stability . it is an urgent need for meeting the growing material and cultural needs of the people and forging closer ties between the party and the government on the one hand and the masses on the other . it is also necessary for implementing tasks of ideological and political work at the grassroots levels .
if the departments concerned can work in close cooperation , coordinate their actions and produce some tangible results in these activities , it will be conducive to promoting the solution of major and difficult issues that the masses feel very strongly about , thus making the effects of ideological and political work felt deep in the heart of the masses , improving the quality of the population as civilized people , and making the urban and rural areas more civilized .
under the new situation , it is necessary to conscientiously implement the important instructions of general secretary of jiang zemin , further improve our ideological understanding and work , and unfold the activities thoroughly , solidly and in a sustained way .
the conference decided that in this year 's activities of " stressing civilization and fostering new practices , " it is necessary to grasp activities of " promoting civilized new practices and making joint efforts to build beautiful homes " with the emphasis on community development while consolidating previous achievements and achieving higher standards .
the main tasks include beautifying the living environment , maintaining public order , enriching people 's cultural and sports life , disseminating scientific knowledge , promoting community service , and cementing closer interpersonal ties .
liu yunshan , executive deputy minister of the central propaganda department and director of the general office of the central guidance committee of spiritual civilization construction , pointed out in his speech : activities of " promoting civilized new practices and making joint efforts to build beautiful homes " must run through the main line of ideological and ethnical education . efforts must be made to improve education in the party 's basic theory , basic line and basic program , improve education in policies concerning the situation , the legal system and the maintenance of social stability , improve education on patriotism , collectivism and socialism , improve education in the spirit of plain living and hard struggle , improve education in marxist materialism and atheism , respecting science and eliminating superstition , and improve education in public mindedness , professional ethics and family values .
liu yunshan emphasized the need to grasp two key points in work . $number task is to develop community services .
residents should be organized and mobilized to give full scope to their strong points and superiorities and take an active part in community mutual - aid services . welfare services catering to the handicapped , the aged , disabled servicemen and family members of martyrs and servicemen , and people in distress in the community should be developed . further efforts should be made to improve the service of community property management departments , business outlets and other service bodies and to gradually explore ways of socializing and industrializing community service .
$number task is to enliven people 's cultural life .
efforts should be made to extensively launch a rich variety of cultural and sports activities and promotions of scientific knowledge that are convenient to the masses . the people should be guided to make conscious efforts to change their old customs and habits and foster healthy and civilized habits .
liu yunshan emphasized the need to do a good job in building three contingents .
$number is the contingent of community volunteer workers . community volunteer worker centers should be gradually established and perfected . their job is to mobilize the community to take an active part in volunteer activities .
$number is the contingent of cultural and sports instructors . cultural and sports activists among the masses should be given ideological education and vocational training , and the more outstanding ones should be selected to serve as instructors for community cultural and sports activities in order to gradually bring these activities onto the track of organized , standardized and healthy development .
$number is the contingent of popular science publicists . while fully bring into play the role of full - and part - time popular science workers , positive efforts should be made to organize retried scientific and technological workers and undergraduates into volunteer groups to disseminate scientific and technological knowledge in the community and give guidance in popular science promotions .
in the building of these contingents , special attention should be paid to bringing into play the role of retired party members , cadres , teachers and workers as well as old labor models in conducting ideological education .
finally , liu yunshan emphatically pointed out : in deeply launching activities of " stressing civilization and fostering new practices , " it is necessary to grasp well the following four issues : $number , full reliance on the masses .
centering round problems that the masses feel strongly about and urgently need to be resolved , care should be taken to design suitable carriers , extensively attract the involvement of the masses , and do more good and tangible things for the masses so that the masses can achieve real benefits .
$number , the proper building of positions .
garrison units should be encouraged to share their cultural and sports grounds and facilities with members of the public while stepping up the building of community facilities .
$number , persistence in making joint efforts to grasp problems and exercise management .
the role of relevant functional departments should be brought into full play and the enthusiasm of all quarters should be aroused in order to produce a combined force through their coordination and cooperation .
$number , increased media publicity .
efforts should be made to promptly report on the progress of activities , introduce advanced experience , and increase the intensity of media supervision .
responsible officials of the ministry of civil affairs , ministry of public security , ministry of construction , ministry of culture , ministry of health , state administration of physical culture and sports , cyl central committee , all - china federation of women , china association for science and other departments and organizations attended and spoke at the conference .
hu zhenmin , deputy director of the general office of the central guidance committee of spiritual civilization construction , chaired the conference .
the us state department publishes a " human rights report " annually .
it goes without saying that in this wide , wide world , every country has its particular problems and circumstances . if the united states wants to publish a " human rights report , " it should do so about its own domestic conditions .
what is strange about the us " human rights report " is that it is preceded by the word " global . " in other words , the united states wants to judge and criticize the human rights conditions of every other country in the world and even lecture and chide a given country for its human rights conditions .
this hegemonic behavior of posing as the " world 's human rights police " is not only an act of utmost disrespect for human rights but also a serious infringement on other countries ' sovereignty .
what has infuriated people is that in addition to continuing to criticize china for its human rights conditions , the united states cites falungong and other incidents as proof that china 's human rights conditions have " retrogressed " and " deteriorated " in the past year , threatening to present once again a motion to " condemn " china at this year 's un human rights commission in geneva . in addition , because of the us need to achieve its anti - china political goal , hong kong has surprisingly become the target of criticism and attack for its human rights conditions after the reversion . it is truly outrageous .
let 's not discuss for the moment whether the aforementioned accusations are true or false . even if they were true , they were something that fell within the category of the implementation of the " one country , two systems " between hong kong and its motherland . what does it have to do with the government of the united states , a country located on the other side of the ocean ? what right does the us state department have to criticize hong kong as if it were one of the us cities or states ?
more importantly , all those accusations by the us state department are pure fabrications and pure nonsense . on no account do they reflect hong kong 's real situation , where human rights and rule of law have been well protected since its reversion . those accusations can only show americans ' blind arrogance and ignorance .
regarding the request made to the npc to interpret the law , the overwhelming majority of hong kong people and foreigners who are truly concerned about hong kong have come to realize that had the sar government not promptly requested the npc to interpret the law , $number mainlanders would have rushed into hong kong , causing tremendous unbearable impact on hong kong 's basic human rights , including rights in the areas of housing , education , medical service , and social order . precisely as a result of the npc 's interpretation of the law , this kind of dangerous development was avoided , and the human rights of hong kong 's $number people are effectively protected and safeguarded .
regarding these groundless accusations , everyone in hong kong will be able to tell that they are absurd and untrue . undoubtedly , there is a sex industry in hong kong .
" snakeheads " also used hong kong to smuggle people from time to time . however , the sar government , including its police , immigration , and customs departments , has adopted the most severe means to crack down on these crimes . anyone found guilty of these crimes will be promptly arrested , imprisoned , or deported . in addition , the information is immediately sent to relevant countries and regions .
the $number people in hong kong will never allow hong kong to become a " smuggling center " or " crime paradise . "
in contrast , crimes have occurred frequently in the united states . women are being raped every minute . cases of shooting , robbery , and threats are occurring in the subway and street every minute . the united states is notorious as a " paradise of crime " as well as " paradise of democracy . "
