to promote the implementation of the leadership responsibility system for the comprehensive management of public security , to solve prominent public security problems in a to - the - point manner , and to maintain social stability , the central committee for comprehensive management of public security today convened in beijing a joint conference both for analyzing the situation of public security and for discussing the leadership responsibility system for the comprehensive management of public security . the meeting analyzed the situation of public security throughout the country and the situation in implementing the leadership responsibility system for the comprehensive management of public security $date and studied measures for further strengthening work in comprehensively managing public security .
it was reported that last year various localities generally strengthened the comprehensive management of public security , and the situation of public security throughout the country as a whole was stable .
public security problems must not be underestimated , however , particularly because violent crimes such as explosion and gun - related cases remained very prominent ; street crimes such as purse - cutting and snatching increased ; law - breaking and criminal activities of the floating population , particularly the blindly floating population without legitimate identification papers , a proper source of income , and a permanent residence remained at a high rate ; and social evils such as prostitution , gambling , and drugs were spreading in some localities .
in connection with the situation of public security , the meeting suggested : at present , all localities need to continue maintaining a high - pressure posture on serious criminal offenses and make the struggle of " dealing severe blows " even more to the point and productive in terms of practical results ; to carry out deepgoing activities for creating security at the grass - roots level and implement various measures of crime prevention ; to further strengthen work for preventing law - breaking and criminal activities of youngsters ; to further strengthen efforts to wipe out social evils such as prostitution , gambling , and drugs ; and to conscientiously strengthen public security regulation over the floating population .
last year various localities generally raised the degree of attention to implementing the leadership responsibility system for the comprehensive management of public security . in practice , they continually improved the substance of the system , gradually standardized the ways of appraisal , and more earnestly put into effect rewards and punishments to vigorously promote the implementation of various measures for comprehensively managing public security .
in $number provinces , autonomous regions , and municipalities throughout the country , party and government leaders at various levels came forward to sign letters of responsibility for the comprehensive management of public security .
most of the various localities have defined party and government heads as $number responsible persons in comprehensively managing public security .
over the past few years , the various localities have gradually established a motivating and restraining mechanism under the leadership responsibility system that consists of three sequential , complementary segments - - the signing of a letter of responsibility , inspection and appraisal , and giving rewards or administration of punishments - - and have paid special attention to inspection and appraisal as the most important among all focuses .
to strengthen and perfect the motivating and restraining mechanism under the leadership responsibility system , various localities have also gradually set up a system of procedure of the committee for comprehensive management of public security , a system of circulating notices on the situation of public security , a system of assigning areas of responsibility to leading committee members , a system of appraisal and inspection , a system of joint meeting of five departments , a system for investigating important cases , a system of reporting on important circumstances , and a system for supervising and speeding up case investigation and handling to gradually institutionalize and regularize work for implementing the leadership responsibility system .
wang shengjun , secretary general of the central commission on politics and law [ ccpl ] , stressed at the meeting : we must unremittingly carry out the struggle of " dealing severe blows " and centralized punishment and continue to maintain a high - pressure posture on criminal offenses ; must strictly carry out the leadership responsibility system for the comprehensive management of public security and promote the implementation of various working measures ; and must carry out deepgoing activities for creating security at the grass - roots level and put in a lot of effort to seek practical results .
attending the meeting were responsible comrades from the ccpl , the central commission for discipline inspection , the supreme people 's court , the supreme people 's procuratorate , the organization department of the cpc central committee , the ministry of personnel , the ministry of supervision , the ministry of public security , the ministry of justice , and other departments .
beijing , $date ( xinhua ) - - jiang zemin , chairman of the central military commission , signed days ago a decree to promulgate and put into force the " regulations governing education programs of the chinese people 's liberation army [ pla ] 's academies and schools . "
the original " provisional regulations governing the operation of army academies and schools , " which were promulgated $date under the names of the general staff department , the general political department , and the general logistics department , have played an important role in regulating the operation of army academies and schools and in promoting their development . in the wake of profound changes in education programs of our army academies and schools , these provisional regulations no longer suit the development of army academies and schools . thus it is definitely necessary to formulate a new set of " regulations governing education programs of the chinese pla 's academies and schools . "
sticking to the direction prescribed by marxism - leninism , mao zedong thought , deng xiaoping theory , and a series of important expositions by comrade jiang zemin , following the military strategic guideline for the new period , carrying forward the fine traditions in education of our army academies and schools , assimilating advanced experience in the field of education both at home and abroad and from within and without the army , and correctly handling the relations between current and long - term needs and between reformatory and regulatory needs , the current " regulations " cover as widely as possible the major areas of activities of army academies and school .
the " regulations " consist of $number chapters with $number articles .
the " regulations " point out : education programs run by army academies and schools are an important component part of the state 's education undertaking , and the basic means for the training of military professionals .
these " regulations " took effect on the day of promulgation .
the west particularly northwest china is rich in land resources , but plagued by fragile ecological environment such as the scarcity of water resources and worsening and soil erosion problems .
wang shucheng said that the focal points of development of water conservancy in western china include four aspects : firstly , taking improving ecological environment as a fundamental starting point , lay down plan for water conservancy projects . secondly , conduct building irrigation area with water - efficient irrigation as focal point . thirdly , intensify unifying management of valley and area water resources with optimal allocation of water resources as the objective .
fourthly , proceeding from a long - term point of view and consideration of overall situation , carry out cross - region and cross - valley water transfer . these four aspects come to a conclusion of handling well optimal allocation of water resources and making effort in improving level of scientific utilization of water resources .
due to unawareness of effective allocation and scientific utilization of water resources , ecological environment was destroyed by good intentions in making wrong things , from which a lesson must be drawn in the development of water resources in western china .
some similar examples can be found in western china .
water conservancy projects in western areas can be classified as engineering projects and non - engineering projects , wang shucheng said .
every province , municipality , and region will be allocated certain projects in line with special emphasis on local condition .
xinjiang will emphasize on project of controlling talimu ( tarim ) river and regional water while qinghai will emphasize on water transfer project to solve the problem of shortage of water supply to xining and neimenggu will mainly solve the issue of reforming water - efficient irrigation .
