beijing , $date ( xinhua ) - - the central military commission (cmc) recently transmitted the " opinions on extensively carrying out the science and technology training of troops to comprehensively increase the troops ' ability to win in a high - tech war " put forward by the general staff headquarters , and urged all officers and men of the armed forces to make clear the new trends of development of the world 's military revolution , increase the sense of responsibility of performing sacred missions , strive to promote the in - depth development of the science and technology training of troops , and comprehensively increase the troops ' ability to win in a high - tech war .
the cmc pointed out that the " opinions on extensively carrying out the science and technology training of troops to comprehensively increase the troops ' ability to win in a high - tech war " put forward by the general staff headquarters have seriously implemented chairman jiang zemin 's important instructions on making the armed forces strong by means of science and technology and carrying out the science and technology training of troops , comprehensively analyzed the situation facing national security and military struggle , made a deep summary of the new experience in military training in the new period , and provided the basis for deeply carrying out the science and technology training of troops in the entire armed forces .
the cmc emphasized that winning in a high - tech war in the future and maintaining the nature , characteristics and style of the people 's armed forces are the highest political demands of the party on the people 's armed forces in the new period , and are also two historical tasks facing the improvement of the quality of our armed forces .
the science and technology training of troops is the practice of using modern science and technology for organization and training and is the fundamental way to increase the combat effectiveness of troops in the contemporary time .
the entire armed force must fully understand the great significance of the science and technology training of troops , regard it as an urgent strategic task to prepare for military struggle in the new period , make efforts to increase the troops ' ability to win , and promote a leap in quality in the troops ' combat effectiveness through constantly deepening the science and technology training of troops .
the " opinions " demanded the entire armed forces should promote the in - depth development of the science and technology training of troops through carrying out reform and renovation on the basis of inheriting and carrying forward the fine traditions of our armed forces , and should make great efforts to renovate military theories and the contents , methods and mechanisms of training , and to make breakthroughs in crucial issues of the science and technology training of troops to promote the in - depth development of such training .
in the science and technology training of troops , it is necessary to put training on joint operation in an outstanding position , improve the mechanisms for joint operation , lay a solid foundation for joint operation , and deeply explore methods for training in joint campaigns .
the " opinions " demanded that units at all levels should mainly and properly grasp the building of the four contingents of commanders , staff personnel , professional technical personnel and instructors , especially the training and bringing up of a large number of military commanding personnel with high comprehensive quality and great ability to carry out renovation .
it is necessary to earnestly strengthen the organization of , and the guidance to , the science and technology training of troops , grasp the correct direction for such training , increase the combined strength as a whole in the science and technology training of troops , speed up the conversion of new achievements in the science and technology training of troops to combat effectiveness , attach importance to and strengthen political work in the science and technology training of troops , fully arouse the enthusiasm and creativeness of the broad masses of officers and men , and maintain a sustained propelling force for the science and technology training of troops .
