$date , he became deputy secretary of the zhaozhou county cpc committee , heilongjiang , and head of zhaozhou county , vice commissioner of suihua prefecture , and deputy secretary of the suihua prefectural cpc committee and commissioner of suihua prefecture . $date , he became secretary of the mudanjiang city cpc committee , vice governor of heilongjiang province , deputy secretary of the heilongjiang provincial cpc committee and secretary of the harbin city cpc committee . from $date , he was deputy secretary of the heilongjing provincial cpc committee and heilongjiang governor .
