chairman li peng presided over the meeting .
the meeting , in line with the nomination of the state council , appointed tian fengshan as the minister of land and natural resources , and removed zhou yongkang from the post .
president jiang zemin signed presidential order no. $number to release the personnel change .
the meeting $number listened to the report made by wang weicheng , chairman of the npc law committee , on the opinions on revising $number draft version of the npc standing committee 's decision on strengthening economic supervision .
afterward , the meeting approved the decision through voting . the meeting also approved the draft agenda for $number session of $number npc , and decided to submit the agenda to the preparatory meeting of $number session of $number npc for examination . the meeting also approved the draft list of presidium and the secretary - general for $number session of $number npc , and decided to submit the list to the preparatory meeting of $number session of $number npc for examination .
the meeting today also passed in principle the draft work report of the npc standing committee . the draft work report will be revised at the chairmanship meeting in line with the opinions proposed by standing committee members , and then being submitted to $number session of $number npc .
the meeting also passed the namelist of non - voting delegates to $number session of $number npc , and the report on the qualifications of newly elected or added deputies by the credential committee of the standing committee . the meeting also passed the standing committee 's decisions on approving the china - cambodia extradition treaty , china - tunisia treaty on judicial aid to civil and commercial affairs , and the china - tadzhikistan agreement on borders .
