beijing , $date ( xinhua ) - - renmin ribao $date commentator 's article : assigning great importance and earnestly practicing what we advocate - - on developing the " three stresses " at the county ( city ) level in a thorough and down - to - earth manner while the " three stresses " education will soon be comprehensively launched in counties ( cities ) across the country , the members of the standing committee of the central political bureau , responding to a proposal made by comrade jiang zemin , have separately visited seven counties ( cities ) recently , conducted a thorough investigation and study on local " three stresses , " held discussion with grassroots cadres , and directly mobilized the leading cadres of those counties ( cities ) .
their visit has not only greatly inspired and educated local cadres and people , but also evoked warm repercussions among all the party members and the broad masses of the people .
to make the members of the central political bureau standing committee directly handle the " three stresses " work in counties ( cities ) was an important measure taken by the party central committee with comrade jiang zemin as the core to concentrate its attention on party building .
it was $number time in the history of our party building that all the comrades of the central political bureau standing committee , led by the party 's general secretary , visited and stayed in some counties ( cities ) for a period of time and directly handled the party building there .
the direct handling of the " three stresses " in counties ( cities ) by the members of the central political bureau standing committee fully shows the high degree of importance attached by the central authorities to the " three stresses " education and particularly to the " three stresses " in counties ( cities ) .
since the start of the " three stresses " education , the members of the central political bureau standing committee have paid great attention to it , made meticulous arrangements for it , heard a number of reports about it , studied relevant measures and provided timely guidance for it .
as the spring festival has just ended and the " two sessions [ the sessions of the national people 's congress and the chinese people 's political consultation conference ] " will begin soon , the comrades of the central political bureau standing committee have been very busy , but they still spent a comparatively long time on visiting those counties ( cities ) and of handling the " three stresses " there . this fact shows that the central committee is indeed treating the " three stresses " education as a matter of paramount importance among all the important party building tasks .
we must thoroughly study the important speech delivered by comrade jiang zemin at the meeting of the leading cadres of gaozhou city , guangdong province , on the " three stresses " education . we must fully understand the important role of counties ( cities ) in party and state affairs , fully understand the particular importance and necessity of the " three stresses " in counties ( cities ) , enhance our sense of political responsibility and sense of urgency in doing a good job in the " three stresses " in counties ( cities ) , and strive to make the " three stresses " in counties ( cities ) a success .
in attaching a high degree of importance to the " three stresses " in counties ( cities ) , the emphasis should be put on practice and action .
in this regard , the members of the central political bureau standing committee have already set an example for us .
to have a say in guiding the " three stresses " in counties ( cities ) , the comrades of the central political bureau standing committee held discussion with grassroots cadres and veteran comrades , visited the masses , seriously listened to the opinions and voices of all quarters , exchanged views on and explored effective measures , familiarized themselves with what was going on among the people , and obtained $number - hand information .
during the course of handling the " three stresses " in counties ( cities ) , the comrades of the central political bureau standing committee have taken the lead in doing a thoroughgoing and painstaking ideological and political work .
to deal with the party character and party style problems among some county ( city ) leading cadres , the members of the central political bureau standing committee sternly pointed out and seriously criticized the problems and set strict demands for those leading cadres ; and at the same time , they enthusiastically gave those cadres systematic guidance to help the latter correct the problems . as a result , the comrades of those counties ( cities ) , with feelings of deep remorse , have realized the existence and harms of the problems . they have also keenly felt the concern , care and earnest hopes of the party central committee for county ( city ) cadres , and have raised their awareness and sense of urgency with respect to their own " three stresses . "
we must learn from the pragmatic work style displayed by the comrades of the central political bureau standing committee , practice what we advocate , work hard in practice , actively explore the experience and law of the " three stresses " in counties ( cities ) and constantly improve our work quality and standard .
we should resolutely oppose the bad work style of merely writing about or talking about attaching importance , or acting in a perfunctory manner .
counties ( cities ) , being a link between the higher levels and the people , have direct contact with the broad masses and their environment , conditions and existing problems have their own local characteristics .
to make the " three stresses " in counties ( cities ) a success and truly solve their existing conspicuous problems , we must do as the comrades of the central political bureau standing committee did [ original xinhua version reads " follow the example of the comrades of the central political bureau standing committee " ] , go down to counties ( cities ) , go deep into the realities of life , conduct investigation and study , boldly practice , create experience and gain the initiative in work .
the strength of good example is infinitely great .
following the example of the members of the central political bureau standing committee , the comrades of many provincial , autonomous regional , municipal and prefecture ( city ) party committees have , one after another , also gone to counties ( cities ) to directly handle the " three stresses " there . the comrades in counties ( cities ) have greatly raised their awareness of the need in promoting the " three stresses , " all preparations for the " three stresses " work are being stepped up , and a very good momentum of the " three stresses " in counties ( cities ) has emerged .
we must work in accordance with the party central committee 's demand , take advantage of the favorable situation to make progress , and do a good job in arranging , organizing and carrying out the " three stresses " in counties ( cities ) .
