we should continue to maintain close ties with persons of all walks of life in hong kong and macao , give full play to the role of the hong kong and macao members of the cppcc national committee , and strive to maintain long - term stability and prosperity in hong kong and macao .
we should earnestly study and actively explore new ways and methods to perform the work of maintaining friendly contacts abroad in the new situation with a view to further promoting the great unity of chinese people at home and abroad . $number .
giving full play to the important role of the cppcc in developing friendly exchanges with other countries .
according to the overall arrangements for china 's diplomatic work , we should actively and properly develop friendly exchanges with other countries .
we should continue to arrange high - level visits in order to expand the cppcc 's influence abroad . we should maintain and develop existing relations with relevant institutions in other countries and with international organizations , establish new friendly contacts in a planned way , and open up new areas of cooperation . we should continue to give full play to the role of the democratic parties , mass organizations , and representatives of various ethnic groups and circles in society in developing friendly exchanges abroad . we should vigorously do a good job in preparing for the $number annual conference of the " $number century forum . "
