they have expressed their determinations one after another to overcome the narrow mentality of " resting content after attaining a small victory and after becoming just a little better - off than before ; " establish the concept of coordinating efforts with other regions of the country as on a single chessboard , as well as the concept that those who become rich $number should help the latecomers ; vigorously develop the productive forces ; and make greater contributions to the country .
in taicang city , which has ranked as jiangsu 's $number in per capita gnp for many years running , city party secretary xu jianming noted : the mentality of " resting content after attaining a small victory and after becoming just a little better - off than before " is an expression of the small - peasant economy , and has already become an ideological obstacle that hinds the progress of the country 's socialist modernization building . in fact , the $number - year - long process of reform and opening up is precisely a process of constantly breaking away from this mentality of the small - peasant economy . general secretary jiang 's idea of launching the educational activity of " always remembering where our wealth comes from and always remembering to make further progress after becoming better - off " in the country 's developed coastal areas has come out at a good time , and there is no mistaking what the activity is aimed at .
