the state should not consider making war for the sake of war .
beijing , $date (zxs) - - at a news briefing held by $number session of $number national people 's congress (npc) today , spokesman of the session zeng jianhui said china has basically established the anti - corruption legal system and in the future , the npc and its standing committee will continue to strengthen work in this respect .
zeng jianhui said that in anti - corruption work , the npc and its standing committee have formulated one after another the decision on severely cracking down on economic crimes , the supplementary provisions on punishing crimes of corruption and bribery , and the supplementary provisions on punishing smuggling ; and special chapters of the revised criminal law stipulate punishment for crimes of corruption and bribery . these , together with the administrative supervision law , the administrative punishment law and other laws formulated in recent years , have basically formed the anti - corruption legal system .
